t-[9px] font-mono px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/20 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">GATE 2 OF 2</span>\n379 |                     <h2 className=\"text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mt-2 text-white\">Configure Ingestion & Priorities</h2>\n380 |                     <p className=\"text-white/50 text-xs mt-1\">Isolate specific technical targets and security bounds.</p>\n381 |                   </div>\n382 | \n383 |                   <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n384 |                     <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase block\">Existing Data Ingestion Level</label>\n385 |                     <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-5 gap-2.5\">\n386 |                       {DATA_READINESS.map((read) => (\n387 |                         <button\n388 |                           key={read.id}\n389 |                           type=\"button\"\n390 |                           onClick={() => setInputs({ ...inputs, dataReadiness: read.id })}\n391 |                           className={`p-3 rounded-lg border text-left transition flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[95px] ${inputs.dataReadiness === read.id ? \"border-[#009DFF]/50 bg-[#009DFF]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/50 hover:border-white/10\"}`}\n392 |                         >\n393 |                           <div>\n394 |                             <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D]/85 uppercase font-bold block leading-none mb-1\">{read.level}</span>\n395 |                             <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white leading-tight\">{read.label}</h4>\n396 |                           </div>\n397 |                           <p className=\"text-[8px] text-white/40 leading-snug mt-1.5\">{read.desc}</p>\n398 |                         </button>\n399 |                       ))}\n400 |                     </div>\n401 |                   </div>\n402 | \n403 |                   <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n404 |                     <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase block\">Focus Strategic Priorities (Select up to 3)</label>\n405 |                     <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-5 gap-2.5\">\n406 |                       {PRIORITIES.map((prio) => {\n407 |                         const isSelected = inputs.priorities.includes(prio.id);\n408 |                         return (\n409 |                           <button\n410 |                             key={prio.id}\n411 |                             type=\"button\"\n412 |                             onClick={() => {\n413 |                               if (isSelected) {\n414 |                                 if (inputs.priorities.length > 1) {\n415 |                                   setInputs({ ...inputs, priorities: inputs.priorities.filter((p) => p !== prio.id) });\n416 |                                 }\n417 |                               } else {\n418 |                                 if (inputs.priorities.length < 3) {\n419 |                                   setInputs({ ...inputs, priorities: [...inputs.priorities, prio.id] });\n420 |                                 } else {\n421 |                                   alert(\"Priority configurations: select up to 3 focus areas.\");\n422 |                                 }\n423 |                               }\n424 |                             }}\n425 |                             className=\"p-3 rounded-lg border text-left transition flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[95px]\"\n426 |                             style={{ borderColor: isSelected ? prio.color : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.05)\", backgroundColor: isSelected ? `${prio.color}08` : \"transparent\" }}\n427 |                           >\n428 |                             <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n429 |                               <span className=\"text-xs\">{prio.icon}</span>\n430 |                               {isSelected && <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full\" style={{ backgroundColor: prio.color }} />}\n431 |                             </div>\n432 |                             <div>\n433 |                               <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white leading-tight mt-1\">{prio.label}</h4>\n434 |                               <p className=\"text-[8px] text-white/35 leading-tight mt-1\">{prio.desc}</p>\n435 |                             </div>\n436 |                           </button>\n437 |                         );\n438 |                       })}\n439 |                     </div>\n440 |                   </div>\n441 | \n442 |                   <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n443 |                     <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase block\">Target Capital Allocation Range</label>\n444 |                     <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2.5\">\n445 |                       {BUDGET_RANGES.map((b) => (\n446 |                         <button\n447 |                           key={b.id}\n448 |                           type=\"button\"\n449 |                           onClick={() => setInputs({ ...inputs, budgetRange: b.id })}\n450 |                           className={`p-3 rounded-lg border text-left transition ${inputs.budgetRange === b.id ? \"border-[#009DFF]/50 bg-[#009DFF]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/50 hover:border-white/10\"}`}\n451 |                         >\n452 |                           <h4 className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-white leading-tight\">{b.label}</h4>\n453 |                           <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 mt-1 leading-none\">{b.desc}</p>\n454 |                         </button>\n455 |                       ))}\n456 |                     </div>\n457 |                   </div>\n458 |                 </div>\n459 | \n460 |               )}\n461 | \n462 |               <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-6 mt-8 flex justify-between items-center\">\n463 |                 <button type=\"button\" onClick={() => setActiveStepGate(1)} disabled={activeStepGate === 1} className={`px-4 h-9 rounded-lg border text-xs font-semibold uppercase flex items-center gap-1 transition ${activeStepGate === 1 ? \"border-white/5 text-white/10\" : \"border-white/10 text-white hover:bg-white/5\"}`}>Back</button>\n464 |                 {activeStepGate === 1 ? (\n465 |                   <button type=\"button\" onClick={() => { if (!inputs.companyName.trim()) { alert(\"Please provide your Organization Name.\"); return; } setActiveStepGate(2); }} className=\"px-5 h-9 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold uppercase bg-[#009DFF] text-black hover:bg-[#009DFF]/90 font-mono shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.25)]\">Next Gate</button>\n466 |                 ) : (\n467 |                   <button type=\"button\" onClick={handleCompile} className=\"px-5 h-9 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold uppercase bg-[#00FF9D] text-black hover:bg-[#00FF9D]/90 font-mono shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,255,157,0.25)]\">Sovereign Compile</button>\n468 |                 )}\n469 |               </div>\n470 |             </div>\n471 | \n472 |           </motion.div>\n473 |         )}\n474 | \n475 |         {step === \"compiling\" && (\n476 |           <motion.div initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.98 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1 }} exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 1.02 }} className=\"max-w-xl mx-auto p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[380px] text-center\" id=\"compiling-container\">\n477 |             <div className=\"relative w-16 h-16 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center\">\n478 |               <div className=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-[#00FF9D]/20 animate-ping\" />\n479 |               <div className=\"absolute inset-2 rounded-full border border-[#009DFF]/30 animate-pulse\" />\n480 |               <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-black border border-[#00FF9D]/80 flex items-center justify-center\">\n481 |                 <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9D] animate-ping\" />\n482 |               </div>\n483 |             </div>\n484 |             <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] font-bold tracking-widest block mb-1\">COMPILING SCHEMA</span>\n485 |             <h2 className=\"text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4\">Structuring Strategic SOW</h2>\n486 |             <div className=\"w-full p-4 rounded-lg bg-black/60 border border-white/5 text-left mb-4 relative overflow-hidden\">\n487 |               <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 h-0.5 bg-[#009DFF] transition-all duration-300\" style={{ width: `${((compilingStepIndex + 1) / compilingMessages.length) * 100}%` }} />\n488 |               <div className=\"flex gap-2 font-mono text-[9px] text-white/50\">\n489 |                 <span className=\"text-[#009DFF]\">&gt;</span>\n490 |                 <p className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-semibold leading-relaxed\">{compilingMessages[compilingStepIndex]}</p>\n491 |               </div>\n492 |             </div>\n493 |             <p className=\"text-white/30 text-[9px] font-mono\">ZERO RETENTION LAYER ACTIVE</p>\n494 |           </motion.div>\n495 |         )}\n496 | \n497 | \n498 |         {step === \"preview\" && (\n499 |           <motion.div initial={{ opacity: 0 }} animate={{ opacity: 1 }} className=\"space-y-6\" id=\"preview-workspace-container\">\n500 |             <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n501 |               <div className=\"lg:col-span-3 space-y-4 sticky top-6 print:hidden\" id=\"workspace-navigator\">\n502 |                 <div className=\"p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 text-left\">\n503 |                   <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/35 font-bold block mb-3\">DOSSIER INDEX</span>\n504 |                   <nav className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n505 |                     {[\n506 |                       \"executive-summary\", \"challenge-statement\", \"recommended-gff-path\", \"proposed-workstreams\",\n507 |                       \"90-day-roadmap\", \"suggested-squad\", \"governance-approach\", \"success-measures\",\n508 |                       \"assumptions\", \"risks\", \"next-steps\"\n509 |                     ].map((id, idx) => {\n510 |                       const label = id.split(\"-\").map(w => w.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + w.slice(1)).join(\" \");\n511 |                       const emojis = [\"📄\", \"🔍\", \"🚀\", \"🗺️\", \"📅\", \"👥\", \"🛡️\", \"📈\", \"📝\", \"⚠️\", \"✍️\"];\n512 |                       return (\n513 |                         <button\n514 |                           key={id}\n515 |                           onClick={() => handleScrollToSection(id)}\n516 |                           className={`w-full text-left px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-[11px] transition flex items-center gap-2 ${activePreviewSection === id ? \"bg-white/5 text-[#009DFF] font-bold border-l border-[#009DFF]\" : \"text-white/50 hover:text-white\"}`}\n517 |                         >\n518 |                           <span>{emojis[idx]}</span>\n519 |                           <span>{idx + 1}. {label}</span>\n520 |                         </button>\n521 |                       );\n522 |                     })}\n523 |                   </nav>\n524 | \n525 |                   <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 space-y-2\">\n526 |                     <button onClick={handleCopyOutline} className=\"w-full py-1.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-white border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 transition text-[9px] font-mono uppercase\">\n527 |                       {copied ? \"✓ Copied\" : \"Copy Outline\"}\n528 |                     </button>\n529 |                     <button onClick={handlePrint} className=\"w-full py-1.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-white border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 transition text-[9px] font-mono uppercase\">\n530 |                       Print Spec Preview\n531 |                     </button>\n532 |                     <button onClick={handleReset} className=\"w-full py-1 text-center text-white/30 text-[9px] font-mono hover:text-white block uppercase\">\n533 |                       [ Clear Forms ]\n534 |                     </button>\n535 |                   </div>\n536 |                 </div>\n537 | \n538 |                 <div className=\"p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/80 text-[10px] text-white/40 space-y-2 text-left\">\n539 |                   <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n540 |                     <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">WORKSPACE</span>\n541 |                     <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono bg-[#E4000F]/15 text-[#E4000F] px-1 rounded font-bold\">LOCKED</span>\n542 |                   </div>\n543 |                   <h4 className=\"font-bold text-white\">Full SOW & Presentation Exports</h4>\n544 |                   <p className=\"font-light leading-snug\">Generate enterprise PPT slide decks and contract SOW templates matching your inputs.</p>\n545 |                   <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n546 |                     <button disabled className=\"flex-1 py-1 rounded bg-white/5 text-white/20 text-[8px] font-mono cursor-not-allowed\">EXPORT PPT</button>\n547 |                     <button disabled className=\"flex-1 py-1 rounded bg-white/5 text-white/20 text-[8px] font-mono cursor-not-allowed\">EXPORT PDF</button>\n548 |                   </div>\n549 |                 </div>\n550 |               </div>\n551 | \n552 |               <div className=\"lg:col-span-9 p-6 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/85 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden print:bg-white print:text-black print:p-0\" id=\"proposal-document-content\">\n553 |                 <div className=\"hidden print:block text-right text-[8px] font-mono text-black/40 mb-6 border-b border-black/10 pb-1\">\n554 |                   <span>GFF AI CONFIDENTIAL PORTFOLIO // SOVEREIGN SPECIFICATION ARCHITECTURE</span>\n555 |                 </div>\n556 | \n557 |                 <div className=\"border-b border-white/10 pb-6 mb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-4 print:border-black/20\">\n558 |                   <div className=\"space-y-2 text-left\">\n559 |                     <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n560 |                       <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9D] print:bg-black\" />\n561 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase print:text-black/60 font-semibold\">PROPOSAL OUTLINE SPECIFICATION</span>\n562 |                     </div>\n563 |                     <h1 className=\"text-xl lg:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight print:text-black font-bold\">Sovereign Multi-Agent Topology</h1>\n564 |                     <p className=\"text-white/60 text-xs font-light max-w-lg print:text-black/70\">\n565 |                       Tailored Technical deployment blueprint and SOW outline for <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.org}</strong>.\n566 |                     </p>\n567 |                   </div>\n568 | \n569 |                   <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 flex flex-col items-end text-right min-w-[170px] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5\">\n570 |                     <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">HORIZON TARGET</span>\n571 |                     <span className=\"text-base font-bold text-white font-mono print:text-black\">{pData.totalWeeks} WEEKS</span>\n572 |                     <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] mt-0.5 uppercase font-bold\">{pData.licenseCost}</span>\n573 |                   </div>\n574 |                 </div>\n575 | \n576 |                 <div className=\"space-y-12 print:space-y-10 text-left\" id=\"document-sections-container\">\n577 |                   <div id=\"executive-summary\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n578 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n579 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION I</span>\n580 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">📄 Executive Summary</h2>\n581 |                     </div>\n582 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-3 print:text-black/85\">\n583 |                       <p>\n584 |                         This document details the sovereign architecture mapped for deploying a custom GFF AI multi-agent cognitive fleet within the infrastructure boundary of <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.org}</strong>. Operating inside the <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.industry}</strong> sector, GFF will deploy a dedicated single-tenant virtual cloud boundary (VPC) that ensures complete compliance with zero data retention benchmarks.\n585 |                       </p>\n586 |                       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] flex justify-between items-center print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/[0.01]\">\n587 |                         <div className=\"text-left\">\n588 |                           <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block print:text-black/50 font-semibold\">SECURITY PROFILE ENFORCED</span>\n589 |                           <p className=\"text-white/80 text-[10px] font-light print:text-black\">Hardened Single-Tenant Private VPC boundary featuring real-time telemetry consensus nodes.</p>\n590 |                         </div>\n591 |                         <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n592 |                           <div className=\"text-center p-2 rounded bg-black/40 min-w-[80px] border border-white/5 print:border-black/10\">\n593 |                             <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#00FF9D] block font-mono print:text-black\">100%</span>\n594 |                             <span className=\"text-[6px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase print:text-black/60\">Isolated</span>\n595 |                           </div>\n596 |                           <div className=\"text-center p-2 rounded bg-black/40 min-w-[80px] border border-white/5 print:border-black/10\">\n597 |                             <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#009DFF] block font-mono print:text-black\">0</span>\n598 |                             <span className=\"text-[6px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase print:text-black/60\">Persistent Logs</span>\n599 |                           </div>\n600 |                         </div>\n601 |                       </div>\n602 |                       <p>\n603 |                         Our proposal details a timeline of <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.totalWeeks} Weeks</strong> utilizing our standard Garage-Foundry-Factory methodology. By integrating local memory caching with GFF’s custom supervisor watchdog topologies, the system removes multi-tenant API dependencies, processing all corporate workloads entirely in-memory.\n604 |                       </p>\n605 |                     </div>\n606 |                   </div>\n607 | \n608 |                   <div id=\"challenge-statement\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n609 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n610 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION II</span>\n611 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">🔍 Challenge Statement</h2>\n612 |                     </div>\n613 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-3 print:text-black/85\">\n614 |                       <p>\n615 |                         Organizations inside the <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.industry}</strong> sector face persistent constraints: high-frequency operational bottlenecks, legacy mainframes with manual query steps, and high compliance liabilities when processing customer identifiers in third-party clouds. At {pData.org}’s current <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.companyScale}</strong> footprint, this introduces severe coordination friction.\n616 |                       </p>\n617 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3.5\">\n618 |                         <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/30 print:border-black/10\">\n619 |                           <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1\">Operational & Pipeline Inefficiencies</h4>\n620 |                           <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 leading-relaxed print:text-black/77 text-left\">\n621 |                             {pData.dataReadinessId === \"raw\" \n622 |                               ? \"Corporate metrics remain trapped in unindexed, unstructured legacy raw silos. This mandates high-latency manual context copying, slowing down standard decision cycles from minutes to days.\"\n623 |                               : \"Despite existing database tables, lack of centralized semantic vector caches blocks cognitive models from immediate, clean context retrieval, resulting in slow relational query overrides.\"\n624 |                             }\n625 |                           </p>\n626 |                         </div>\n627 |                         <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/30 print:border-black/10\">\n628 |                           <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1\">Data Exposure & Retention Liability</h4>\n629 |                           <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 leading-relaxed print:text-black/77 text-left\">\n630 |                             Standard multi-tenant public AI configurations require client request payloads to persist on third-party servers for safety audits and fine-tuning. This constitutes a severe intellectual property compliance liability.\n631 |                           </p>\n632 |                         </div>\n633 |                       </div>\n634 |                     </div>\n635 |                   </div>\n636 | \n637 |                   <div id=\"recommended-gff-path\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n638 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n639 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION III</span>\n640 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">🚀 Recommended GFF Path</h2>\n641 |                     </div>\n642 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n643 |                       <p>\n644 |                         GFF recommends configuring a private virtual enclave inside your single-tenant space. We deploy specialized GFF sovereign agent topologies that process transaction tokens directly inside isolated memory buffers with zero external persistence pipelines.\n645 |                       </p>\n646 | \n647 |                       {/* DIAGRAM METAPHOR */}\n648 |                       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-[#009DFF]/20 bg-[#030305] text-left relative print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5\">\n649 |                         <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono text