{"ts":"2026-06-26T21:12:18.773Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Defining State Structure**\n\nI'm making progress on structuring the input state within `app/build/proposal/page.tsx`. Currently, I'm focusing on crafting a clean state structure that accommodates optional fields like organization or company name, alongside robust validation logic. The goal is to provide a clean and maintainable foundation for this complex page.\n\n\n**Refining Industry Categories**\n\nI'm now refining the industry categories I'll be supporting. I've decided to keep the existing, enterprise-focused options: Banking & Finance, Insurance, Healthcare, Telecom, and Public Sector. I'm also planning to extend `INDUSTRIES` with broader options to ensure comprehensive coverage. I'm taking a close look at the existing industry definitions in `components/build/types.ts` to inform this expansion. I'll need to define additional options to make sure all bases are nicely covered.\n\n\n**Expanding Industry Definitions**\n\nI'm expanding the industry definitions in `app/build/proposal/page.tsx`, and I've come up with a richer set of options now. I'm focusing on defining an expanded range of enterprise sectors to cover more ground. I'm also planning to create a set of custom challenge and outcome options for users to select from. I'm focusing on these custom challenges: \"data-fragmentation,\" \"cost-explosion,\" \"compliance-risk,\" \"operational-latency,\" and \"cognitive-scalability,\" and these custom outcomes: \"zero-retention\"\n\n\n**Defining Engagement Paths**\n\nI'm now defining the engagement paths. I have `garage`, `foundry`, `factory`, and `operate` to allow for options that range from co-innovation to industrial-scale orchestration. I'm also planning to create a set of target timelines. These timelines will range from a 30-day sandbox pilot to continuous adaptive co-run.\n\n**Setting Validation Gates**\n\nI'm now establishing validation gates. The goal is to ensure data integrity at each stage of the new forms. This will let users confirm key inputs. This is essential for maintaining data quality and user experience.\n\n\n**Establishing Validation Gates**\n\nI'm now creating validation logic for the form's steps, focusing on Gates 2 and 3. Gate 2 confirms selections for `primaryChallenge`, `priorityOutcomes`, and `targetTimeline`. Gate 3 validates the `preferredEngagementPath`. I'm using these gates to ensure data integrity and a smooth user experience. This design provides clear feedback and a sense of progression.\n\n\n\n**Designing Form Enhancements**\n\nI'm now designing visual improvements, focusing on interactive elements. I'm aiming for sleek cards for company size and an optional geography input. Step 2 includes interactive selection cards for the primary challenge, multiple-choice outcomes, and a timeline selector. Step 3 involves styled cards for engagement pathways. I'm focusing on a polished and responsive design.\n\n\n**Designing Engagement Cards**\n\nI'm finalizing the Figma design, focusing on high-contrast card headers with engagement specifics and core outcomes. I'm incorporating subtle glowing borders for active selections and defining budget range cards. I'm also adding interactive stakeholder input with tag suggestions. Next, I'm working on the live outline preview side panel.\n\n\n\n**Defining Compile Transition**\n\nI'm now detailing the \"Sovereign Compile\" transition with a terminal-style loader, which will include a sequence of log messages to give the user the feel of a \"live, behind-the-scenes\" process. I'm focusing on messages that reflect the real underlying actions. These include initializing the compiler, applying industry overrides, constructing resource budgets, injecting timeline constraints, designing architecture boundaries, enforcing retention pipelines, and finalizing the SOW. This should make the page feel engaging!\n\n\n**Defining Proposal Viewer**\n\nI'm now detailing the proposal viewer's design for the preview step, aiming for a stunning user experience. I'm focusing on a left-side navigation sidebar for quick section access. In the center, there will be an interactive, printable Statement of Work (SOW) document with an editorial design. It will have a custom header with organization, industry, and scale details. Section 1 will be an executive summary, Section 2 covers engagement models, and Section 3 details project phases and the timeline.\n\n\n**Defining Proposal Contents**\n\nI'm now detailing the remaining sections of the proposal viewer, focusing on key elements. I'm prioritizing the inclusion of technical deliverables and \"Administrative Boundaries\" for entered stakeholders. Section 5 will present a structured capital allocation table if a budget range is selected, or standard pricing brackets otherwise. Section 6 will display real-time telemetry based on user selections. I'm also implementing an interactive signature block with a timestamped compliance seal.\n\n\n**Refining Imports and Definitions**\n\nI'm now refining the import statements and definitions in `app/build/proposal/page.tsx`. I've confirmed that `ToolPageShell` and `ToolHero` are excellent components, so I'll be keeping them. I'm focusing on defining `INDUSTRIES`, `COMPANY_SIZES`, `CHALLENGES`, `OUTCOMES`, and `TIMELINES`. I'm using appropriate emojis, descriptions, and IDs.\n\n\n**Defining Proposal Intakes**\n\nI'm now defining the interface for proposal inputs in `app/build/proposal/page.tsx`, and I've focused on `ProposalIntakeInputs`. It includes fields like `companyName`, `industry`, `companySize`, and engagement-specific details. I'm taking care to cover both required and optional fields. I'm also addressing the custom challenge flow, ensuring the user can input the `customChallenge` if `primaryChallenge` is \"other\".\n\n\n**Initializing Input Defaults**\n\nI'm now initializing the input defaults within `app/build/proposal/page.tsx` with high-fidelity values to streamline testing. I've pre-populated the form with sensible choices, including an initial `ProposalIntakeInputs` object. This makes for a more efficient workflow as I focus on the design of the form. I'm taking care to ensure linting issues are handled.\n\n\n**Reviewing Code Structure**\n\nI'm now running through the code, focusing on the proposed structure. I'm taking a close look at the imports, constants, state hooks, and step navigation. I'm reviewing the dynamic proposal data generator helper function and the layout, paying close attention to the guided intake form and the Live Outline preview. I'm making sure all elements are in place, particularly Next.js Link elements.\n\n\n**Designing SVG Topology**\n\nI'm now designing an incredible, responsive SVG diagram. I'm building a component within the page to render a custom VPC architecture based on the chosen engagement model. For `garage`, it will be a \"Sandbox Discovery Tunnel\"; for `foundry`, a \"Hardened VPC Core Enclave\"; for `factory`, a \"Sovereign Multi-Region Agent Fleet\"; and for `operate`, an \"Active Telemetry SLA Watchdog Bridge.\" I'm really excited about this.\n\n\n**Designing Code Composition**\n\nI'm now focusing on a complete refactor, aiming for a premium, frontend-only Proposal Builder. My plan is to replace the entire file to add all requested fields, structure the multi-step form, and include interactive GFF engagement path cards. A live outline preview and compiled SOW view will also be incorporated. Overwriting is the cleanest, safest approach to avoid potential overlaps or broken tags, so I'll be careful to craft the code perfectly.\n\n\n**Defining Engagement Paths**\n\nI'm now detailing the engagement path definitions within the codebase. I'm focusing on the GFF Garage, Foundry, and Factory paths, defining their titles, narrative, deliverables, and SOW scope details for a better user experience. These include custom engineering, platform builds, and industrial-scale orchestration.\n\n\n**Defining Budget Ranges**\n\nI'm now defining the budget ranges, creating options for \"Seed Incubator,\" \"Scale Foundry,\" and \"Enterprise Factory.\" I've specified details for each, including associated use cases and typical engagements. These range from proof-of-concepts to global deployments, giving users a clear scope to work with.\n\n\n**Refining Output Generation**\n\nI'm now refining the `generateProposalData()` function. I'm focusing on incorporating geography if provided and ensuring the custom outputs are highly tailored to user inputs. I'm also ensuring the compilation screen terminal log is crisp and technical with beautiful, real-time-feeling messages. I'm taking care to use local state with safe hydration checks.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T21:12:18.777Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"d2rgudjp","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/build/proposal/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect, useRef } from \"react\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\";\nimport { ToolPageShell, ToolHero } from \"@/components/build/components\";\nimport { Industry, CompanySize } from \"@/components/build/types\";\n\n// ==========================================\n// 1. Metadata & Definitions for Intake Flow\n// ==========================================\n\nconst INDUSTRIES: { id: Industry; label: string; icon: string; desc: string }[] = [\n  { id: \"banking\", label: \"Banking & Finance\", icon: \"🏦\", desc: \"Sovereign ledgers, AML auditing, and transaction validation.\" },\n  { id: \"insurance\", label: \"Insurance\", icon: \"🛡️\", desc: \"Automated underwriting, fraud context extraction, and risk auditing.\" },\n  { id: \"healthcare\", label: \"Healthcare & Pharma\", icon: \"🏥\", desc: \"HIPAA pipeline guardrails, clinical context synthesis, and EMR search.\" },\n  { id: \"telecom\", label: \"Telecom & Networks\", icon: \"📡\", desc: \"Telemetry monitoring, real-time SLA watchdogs, and routing orchestration.\" },\n  { id: \"public-sector\", label: \"Public Sector & Defense\", icon: \"🏛️\", desc: \"Sovereign cloud administration, air-gapped enclaves, and policy compliance.\" },\n  { id: \"energy\", label: \"Energy & Mining\", icon: \"⚡\", desc: \"IoT grid optimization, physical asset telemetry, and predictive safety models.\" }\n];\n\nconst COMPANY_SIZES: { id: CompanySize; label: string; desc: string; range: string }[] = [\n  { id: \"small\", label: \"Sandbox Incubator\", desc: \"Rapid validation, low-overhead deployments, focused pilot scope.\", range: \"1 - 99 Members\" },\n  { id: \"medium\", label: \"Mid-Market Growth\", desc: \"Regional enterprise coverage, cross-system compliance pipelines.\", range: \"100 - 999 Members\" },\n  { id: \"enterprise\", label: \"Enterprise Scale\", desc: \"Global multi-region infrastructure, advanced compliance boundaries.\", range: \"1,000 - 9,999 Members\" },\n  { id: \"global-conglomerate\", label: \"Global Conglomerate\", desc: \"Air-gapped security enclaves, multi-tenant network partitioning.\", range: \"10,000+ Members\" }\n];\n\nconst CHALLENGES = [\n  { id: \"data-fragmentation\", label: \"Data Fragmentation\", icon: \"🗄️\", desc: \"Metrics trapped inside unindexed, unstructured legacy silos blocking AI access.\" },\n  { id: \"compliance-risk\", label: \"Compliance & Leakage Risk\", icon: \"🔒\", desc: \"External SaaS telemetry leaks private IP. Mandates single-tenant isolated enclaves.\" },\n  { id: \"operational-latency\", label: \"Operational Loop Latency\", icon: \"⏳\", desc: \"Manual document routing, verification steps, and reporting slowing down cycles.\" },\n  { id: \"cost-explosion\", label: \"API & SaaS Cost Explosion\", icon: \"📈\", desc: \"Skyrocketing token consumption fees, unstructured billing, and overlapping tooling.\" },\n  { id: \"other\", label: \"Custom Strategic Obstacle\", icon: \"⚙️\", desc: \"Provide a custom corporate obstacle or technical constraint to resolve.\" }\n];\n\nconst OUTCOMES = [\n  { id: \"zero-retention\", label: \"Zero Retention VPC\", desc: \"Absolute secure pipelines with zero memory logging boundaries.\" },\n  { id: \"sub-150ms-latency\", label: \"Sub-150ms Execution\", desc: \"Dynamic cognitive agents performing sub-second decision loops.\" },\n  { id: \"cost-reclamation\", label: \"30%+ Expense Reclamation\", desc: \"Replace fragile external APIs with highly optimized local open models.\" },\n  { id: \"telemetry-audit\", label: \"Real-Time Telemetry Audit\", desc: \"Continuous, automatic compliance validation ledger tracks all queries.\" },\n  { id: \"fleet-orchestration\", label: \"Multi-Agent Fleet Orchestration\", desc: \"Deploy interconnected cognitive nodes working across corporate layers.\" }\n];\n\nconst TIMELINES = [\n  { id: \"30-days\", label: \"30-Day Sandbox Pilot\", desc: \"High-speed validation, limited sandbox scope, co-innovation sprint.\", weeks: 4 },\n  { id: \"90-days\", label: \"90-Day Production SOW\", desc: \"Full-scale core deployment, VPC isolation, primary systems integration.\", weeks: 12 },\n  { id: \"180-days\", label: \"180-Day Federated Rollout\", desc: \"Multi-department rollout, custom fine-tuning, cross-region peering.\", weeks: 24 },\n  { id: \"continuous\", label: \"Continuous SLA Co-Run\", desc: \"Persistent system optimization, regular compliance updates, proactive tuning.\", weeks: 52 }\n];\n\nconst ENGAGEMENT_PATHS = [\n  {\n    id: \"garage\" as const,\n    label: \"GFF Garage\",\n    badge: \"Co-Innovation Sprint\",\n    desc: \"Rapid discovery, sandboxed design, and validation proof-of-concept. Perfect for high-speed strategic alignment.\",\n    weeks: \"2 - 4 Weeks\",\n    squad: \"1 Architect, 1 Engineer\",\n    outcome: \"Validated Interactive Prototype & Baseline Architecture Blueprint\",\n    accent: \"#009DFF\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"foundry\" as const,\n    label: \"GFF Foundry\",\n    badge: \"Bespoke Platform build\",\n    desc: \"Custom engineering, model optimization, and private VPC deployment. The standard choice for secure systems construction.\",\n    weeks: \"6 - 12 Weeks\",\n    squad: \"1 Lead Architect, 2 Systems Engineers, 1 Security Specialist\",\n    outcome: \"Hardened Single-Tenant Platform deployed inside private cloud\",\n    accent: \"#00FF9D\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"factory\" as const,\n    label: \"GFF Factory\",\n    badge: \"Industrial Scale Fleets\",\n    desc: \"High-volume cognitive agent orchestration, automated pipelines, and enterprise-wide federated data mesh networks.\",\n    weeks: \"12 - 24 Weeks\",\n    squad: \"2 Architects, 4 Core Engineers, 1 QA Auditor, 1 Delivery Director\",\n    outcome: \"Multi-agent automated workforce operating across production databases\",\n    accent: \"#9D00FF\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"operate\" as const,\n    label: \"GFF Operate\",\n    badge: \"SLA-Driven Co-Run\",\n    desc: \"Continuous proactive monitoring, scheduled compliance updates, model weight updates, and guaranteed performance SLAs.\",\n    weeks: \"Ongoing Execution\",\n    squad: \"Dedicated Site Reliability Fleet, Lead AI Performance Engineer\",\n    outcome: \"Guaranteed 99.9% uptime, compliance reports, and proactive optimizations\",\n    accent: \"#E5A93C\"\n  }\n];\n\nconst BUDGET_RANGES = [\n  { id: \"tier-1\", label: \"Discovery Capital ($50K - $250K)\", desc: \"Suited for GFF Garage exploration and sandbox verification.\" },\n  { id: \"tier-2\", label: \"Strategic Platform ($250K - $1M)\", desc: \"Optimal for core GFF Foundry setup and VPC deployments.\" },\n  { id: \"tier-3\", label: \"Industrial Scale ($1M+)\", desc: \"Required for GFF Factory federated rollouts and persistent co-run.\" }\n];\n\n// ==========================================\n// 2. Types & Interface\n// ==========================================\n\ninterface ProposalIntakeInputs {\n  companyName: string;\n  industry: Industry;\n  companySize: CompanySize;\n  primaryChallenge: string;\n  customChallenge: string;\n  priorityOutcomes: string[];\n  targetTimeline: string;\n  preferredEngagementPath: \"garage\" | \"foundry\" | \"factory\" | \"operate\";\n  budgetRange: string;\n  geography: string;\n  stakeholders: string;\n}\n\nconst INITIAL_INTAKE_INPUTS: ProposalIntakeInputs = {\n  companyName: \"\",\n  industry: \"banking\",\n  companySize: \"enterprise\",\n  primaryChallenge: \"compliance-risk\",\n  customChallenge: \"\",\n  priorityOutcomes: [\"zero-retention\", \"sub-150ms-latency\"],\n  targetTimeline: \"90-days\",\n  preferredEngagementPath: \"foundry\",\n  budgetRange: \"tier-2\",\n  geography: \"\",\n  stakeholders: \"\"\n};\n\nexport default function ProposalBuilderPage() {\n  const [inputs, setInputs] = useState<ProposalIntakeInputs>(INITIAL_INTAKE_INPUTS);\n  const [step, setStep] = useState<\"configure\" | \"compiling\" | \"preview\">(\"configure\");\n  const [activeStepGate, setActiveStepGate] = useState<1 | 2 | 3>(1);\n  const [compilingStepIndex, setCompilingStepIndex] = useState(0);\n  const [copied, setCopied] = useState(false);\n  const [saved, setSaved] = useState(false);\n  const [hasSavedDraft, setHasSavedDraft] = useState(false);\n  const [activePreviewSection, setActivePreviewSection] = useState<string>(\"executive-summary\");\n  const [signName, setSignName] = useState(\"\");\n  const [signTitle, setSignTitle] = useState(\"\");\n  const [isSigned, setIsSigned] = useState(false);\n  const [mounted, setMounted] = useState(false);\n\n  // Simple validation messages\n  const [validationErrors, setValidationErrors] = useState<Record<string, string>>({});\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    setMounted(true);\n    if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") {\n      const draft = localStorage.getItem(\"gff_proposal_draft_intake\");\n      if (draft) setHasSavedDraft(true);\n    }\n  }, []);\n\n  const compilingMessages = [\n    \"Spinning up local compiler sandbox...\",\n    \"Querying GFF strategic taxonomy parameters...\",\n    \"Applying regulatory compliance standards override...\",\n    \"Sizing GFF delivery squad parameters...\",\n    \"Configuring isolated virtual boundary rules...\",\n    \"Enforcing strict zero-data retention pipelines...\",\n    \"Generating premium SOW specifications...\"\n  ];\n\n  const validateStep = (gate: 1 | 2 | 3): boolean => {\n    const errors: Record<string, string> = {};\n    if (gate === 1) {\n      if (!inputs.industry) errors.industry = \"Please select a primary industry vertical.\";\n      if (!inputs.companySize) errors.companySize = \"Please specify company scale.\";\n    } else if (gate === 2) {\n      if (!inputs.primaryChallenge) errors.primaryChallenge = \"Please identify your primary business challenge.\";\n      if (inputs.primaryChallenge === \"other\" && !inputs.customChallenge.trim()) {\n        errors.customChallenge = \"Please specify your custom corporate obstacle.\";\n      }\n      if (inputs.priorityOutcomes.length === 0) {\n        errors.priorityOutcomes = \"Please select at least one priority target outcome.\";\n      }\n      if (!inputs.targetTimeline) errors.targetTimeline = \"Please select a target timeline.\";\n    } else if (gate === 3) {\n      if (!inputs.preferredEngagementPath) errors.preferredEngagementPath = \"Please select an engagement pathway.\";\n    }\n\n    setValidationErrors(errors);\n    return Object.keys(errors).length === 0;\n  };\n\n  const handleNextGate = () => {\n    if (validateStep(activeStepGate)) {\n      setActiveStepGate((prev) => (prev + 1) as 1 | 2 | 3);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleCompile = () => {\n    if (!validateStep(3)) return;\n    setStep(\"compiling\");\n    setCompilingStepIndex(0);\n  };\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (step !== \"compiling\") return;\n    const interval = setInterval(() => {\n      setCompilingStepIndex((prev) => {\n        if (prev < compilingMessages.length - 1) return prev + 1;\n        clearInterval(interval);\n        setStep(\"preview\");\n        return prev;\n      });\n    }, 450);\n    return () => clearInterval(interval);\n  }, [step]);\n\n  const handleSaveDraft = () => {\n    if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") {\n      localStorage.setItem(\"gff_proposal_draft_intake\", JSON.stringify(inputs));\n      setSaved(true);\n      setHasSavedDraft(true);\n      setTimeout(() => setSaved(false), 2000);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleRestoreDraft = () => {\n    if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") {\n      const draft = localStorage.getItem(\"gff_proposal_draft_intake\");\n      if (draft) {\n        setInputs(JSON.parse(draft));\n        setHasSavedDraft(false);\n      }\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleReset = () => {\n    setInputs(INITIAL_INTAKE_INPUTS);\n    setStep(\"configure\");\n    setActiveStepGate(1);\n    setIsSigned(false);\n    setSignName(\"\");\n    setSignTitle(\"\");\n    setValidationErrors({});\n    if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") {\n      localStorage.removeItem(\"gff_proposal_draft_intake\");\n      setHasSavedDraft(false);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handlePrint = () => {\n    if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") window.print();\n  };\n\n  const handleCopyOutline = () => {\n    const data = generateProposalData();\n    const outlineText = `GFF AI SOVEREIGN INTEGRATION PROPOSAL\n----------------------------------------\nOrganization Name: ${data.org}\nSector Vertical: ${data.industryLabel}\nOperational Footprint: ${data.companySizeLabel}\nGeographic Deployment: ${data.geographyLabel}\nPriority Challenge: ${data.challengeLabel}\nTarget Path: ${data.engagementPathObj.label} (${data.engagementPathObj.badge})\nProject Scope Timeline: ${data.timelineLabel} (${data.weeks} Weeks)\nCore Squad Config: ${data.engagementPathObj.squad}\nCapital Allocation Range: ${data.budgetLabel}\nSponsor Stakeholders: ${data.stakeholdersLabel}\n\nKEY DELIVERABLES:\n${data.deliverables.map((d, i) => `${i + 1}. ${d}`).join(\"\\n\")}\n`;\n    navigator.clipboard.writeText(outlineText);\n    setCopied(true);\n    setTimeout(() => setCopied(false), 2000);\n  };\n\n  // ==========================================\n  // 3. Dynamic Proposal Generation Data\n  // ==========================================\n  const generateProposalData = () => {\n    const org = inputs.companyName.trim() || \"Enterprise Client\";\n    const indObj = INDUSTRIES.find((i) => i.id === inputs.industry) || INDUSTRIES[0];\n    const sizeObj = COMPANY_SIZES.find((s) => s.id === inputs.companySize) || COMPANY_SIZES[2];\n    const pathObj = ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.find((p) => p.id === inputs.preferredEngagementPath) || ENGAGEMENT_PATHS[1];\n    const timelineObj = TIMELINES.find((t) => t.id === inputs.targetTimeline) || TIMELINES[1];\n    const budgetObj = BUDGET_RANGES.find((b) => b.id === inputs.budgetRange) || BUDGET_RANGES[1];\n\n    const challengeLabel = inputs.primaryChallenge === \"other\" && inputs.customChallenge.trim()\n      ? inputs.customChallenge.trim()\n      : (CHALLENGES.find((c) => c.id === inputs.primaryChallenge)?.label || \"Sovereign Integration\");\n\n    const geographyLabel = inputs.geography.trim() || \"Global Private VPC Network Perimeter\";\n    const stakeholdersLabel = inputs.stakeholders.trim() || \"Chief Technology Officer, Compliance Committee\";\n\n    // Strategic outcome text translations\n    const selectedOutcomeLabels = inputs.priorityOutcomes.map(\n      (out) => OUTCOMES.find((o) => o.id === out)?.label || out\n    );\n\n    // Calculate dynamic implementation timing\n    let calculatedWeeks = timelineObj.weeks;\n    if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"garage\") calculatedWeeks = 4;\n    else if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"operate\") calculatedWeeks = 52;\n    else {\n      // Modify Foundry/Factory based on scale\n      if (inputs.companySize === \"small\") calculatedWeeks = Math.max(4, calculatedWeeks - 4);\n      else if (inputs.companySize === \"global-conglomerate\") calculatedWeeks = calculatedWeeks + 4;\n    }\n\n    // Phase distribution\n    const p1 = Math.max(1, Math.round(calculatedWeeks * 0.15));\n    const p2 = Math.max(1, Math.round(calculatedWeeks * 0.30));\n    const p3 = Math.max(1, Math.round(calculatedWeeks * 0.40));\n    const p4 = Math.max(1, calculatedWeeks - (p1 + p2 + p3));\n\n    // Dynamic deliverables based on path\n    let deliverables: string[] = [];\n    if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"garage\") {\n      deliverables = [\n        \"Interactive high-velocity client sandbox prototype\",\n        \"Strategic SOW architecture topology outline schema\",\n        \"Initial data pipeline schema risk audit assessment\",\n        \"Targeted performance benchmarking telemetry sheet\"\n      ];\n    } else if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"foundry\") {\n      deliverables = [\n        \"Fully provisioned, isolated single-tenant private VPC perimeter\",\n        \"Tailored multi-agent consensus network and workflow configurations\",\n        \"Hardened OmniMesh read-only legacy data connector pipelines\",\n        \"Enterprise-wide compliance audit ledger logging software\"\n      ];\n    } else if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"factory\") {\n      deliverables = [\n        \"Industrial-scale federated data mesh network connectors\",\n        \"Autonomous auto-scaling cross-department agent fleet systems\",\n        \"Highly integrated compliance watchdog and safety enforcer software\",\n        \"Sovereign multi-region VPC peering configurations\"\n      ];\n    } else {\n      deliverables = [\n        \"Active monitoring uptime and model performance telemetry panels\",\n        \"Guaranteed 99.9% operational performance SLA monitoring setup\",\n        \"Proactive scheduled compliance and data policy updates\",\n        \"Weekly technical optimization analysis reports and audit files\"\n      ];\n    }\n\n    return {\n      org,\n      industryLabel: indObj.label,\n      industryDesc: indObj.desc,\n      industryIcon: indObj.icon,\n      companySizeLabel: sizeObj.label,\n      companySizeDesc: sizeObj.desc,\n      companySizeRange: sizeObj.range,\n      challengeLabel,\n      timelineLabel: timelineObj.label,\n      weeks: calculatedWeeks,\n      engagementPathObj: pathObj,\n      budgetLabel: inputs.budgetRange ? budgetObj.label : \"Tailored Strategic Budget\",\n      geographyLabel,\n      stakeholdersLabel,\n      selectedOutcomeLabels,\n      deliverables,\n      p1, p2, p3, p4\n    };\n  };\n\n  const pData = generateProposalData();\n\n  // ==========================================\n  // 4. Custom SVG Deployment Diagrams\n  // ==========================================\n  const renderTopologyDiagram = (path: \"garage\" | \"foundry\" | \"factory\" | \"operate\") => {\n    switch (path) {\n      case \"garage\":\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-full h-44\" viewBox=\"0 0 600 180\" fill=\"none\">\n            {/* Background elements */}\n            <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"600\" height=\"180\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#030305\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" />\n            <circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"90\" r=\"30\" fill=\"rgba(0,157,255,0.05)\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeDasharray=\"3 3\" />\n            <circle cx=\"300\" cy=\"90\" r=\"30\" fill=\"rgba(0,157,255,0.1)\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            <circle cx=\"500\" cy=\"90\" r=\"30\" fill=\"rgba(0,255,157,0.05)\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeDasharray=\"3 3\" />\n            {/* Connection lines */}\n            <path d=\"M 130 90 L 270 90\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" strokeDasharray=\"4 4\" />\n            <path d=\"M 330 90 L 470 90\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            {/* Labels */}\n            <text x=\"100\" y=\"94\" fill=\"#ffffff\" fontSize=\"9\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">INBOX</text>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"94\" fill=\"#009DFF\" fontSize=\"10\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" fontWeight=\"bold\" textAnchor=\"middle\">SANDBOX CORE</text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"94\" fill=\"#00FF9D\" fontSize=\"9\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">PROTOTYPE</text>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"150\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">CO-INNOVATION GARAGE PIPELINE (HIGH-VELOCITY TRIALS)</text>\n          </svg>\n        );\n      case \"foundry\":\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-full h-44\" viewBox=\"0 0 600 180\" fill=\"none\">\n            <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"600\" height=\"180\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#030305\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" />\n            {/* Isolated Perimeter Box */}\n            <rect x=\"180\" y=\"25\" width=\"240\" height=\"130\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"rgba(0,157,255,0.02)\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"42\" fill=\"#009DFF\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" fontWeight=\"bold\" textAnchor=\"middle\">HARDENED VPC BOUNDARY (SINGLE-TENANT)</text>\n            {/* Internal nodes */}\n            <circle cx=\"240\" cy=\"95\" r=\"20\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n            <circle cx=\"300\" cy=\"95\" r=\"22\" fill=\"rgba(0,255,157,0.05)\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            <circle cx=\"360\" cy=\"95\" r=\"20\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n            {/* Pipelines */}\n            <path d=\"M 60 95 L 180 95\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" strokeWidth=\"1.2\" strokeDasharray=\"3 3\" />\n            <path d=\"M 420 95 L 540 95\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1.2\" />\n            <path d=\"M 260 95 L 278 95\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n            <path d=\"M 322 95 L 340 95\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n            {/* Node labels */}\n            <text x=\"60\" y=\"83\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">OMNIMESH INGESTION</text>\n            <text x=\"240\" y=\"98\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.7)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">AGENT</text>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"98\" fill=\"#00FF9D\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" fontWeight=\"bold\" textAnchor=\"middle\">SUPERVISOR</text>\n            <text x=\"360\" y=\"98\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.7)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">AUDIT</text>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"83\" fill=\"#00FF9D\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">SECURE OUTPUT</text>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"165\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">GFF PRIVATE CORE PLATFORM ARCHITECTURE (ZERO RETENTION)</text>\n          </svg>\n        );\n      case \"factory\":\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-full h-44\" viewBox=\"0 0 600 180\" fill=\"none\">\n            <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"600\" height=\"180\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#030305\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" />\n            {/* Multi-agent grids */}\n            <rect x=\"40\" y=\"45\" width=\"100\" height=\"90\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(157,0,255,0.03)\" stroke=\"#9D00FF\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeDasharray=\"2 2\" />\n            <rect x=\"250\" y=\"45\" width=\"100\" height=\"90\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(157,0,255,0.03)\" stroke=\"#9D00FF\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeDasharray=\"2 2\" />\n            <rect x=\"460\" y=\"45\" width=\"100\" height=\"90\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(157,0,255,0.03)\" stroke=\"#9D00FF\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeDasharray=\"2 2\" />\n            {/* Connectors */}\n            <path d=\"M 140 90 L 250 90\" stroke=\"#9D00FF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            <path d=\"M 350 90 L 460 90\" stroke=\"#9D00FF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            {/* Text labels */}\n            <text x=\"90\" y=\"93\" fill=\"#ffffff\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">DEPT AGENTS A</text>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"93\" fill=\"#9D00FF\" fontSize=\"9\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" fontWeight=\"bold\" textAnchor=\"middle\">ROUTING ENGINE</text>\n            <text x=\"510\" y=\"93\" fill=\"#ffffff\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">DEPT AGENTS B</text>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"28\" fill=\"rgba(157,0,255,0.8)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">FEDERATED INTEGRATION</text>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"162\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">GFF INDUSTRIAL MULTI-AGENT ORCHESTRATION SHIELD</text>\n          </svg>\n        );\n      case \"operate\":\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-full h-44\" viewBox=\"0 0 600 180\" fill=\"none\">\n            <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"600\" height=\"180\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#030305\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" />\n            {/* Monitor wave */}\n            <path d=\"M 30 90 L 150 90 L 180 40 L 210 140 L 240 90 L 320 90 L 335 70 L 350 110 L 365 90 L 570 90\" stroke=\"#E5A93C\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            {/* Indicators */}\n            <circle cx=\"180\" cy=\"40\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#030305\" stroke=\"#E5A93C\" strokeWidth=\"2\" />\n            <circle cx=\"210\" cy=\"140\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#030305\" stroke=\"#E5A93C\" strokeWidth=\"2\" />\n            {/* Overlays */}\n            <text x=\"180\" y=\"28\" fill=\"#E5A93C\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">LATENCY GUARD</text>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"153\" fill=\"#E5A93C\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">COMPLIANCE WATCHDOG</text>\n            <text x=\"300\" y=\"165\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">GFF SLA REAL-TIME ACTIVE MONITORING & ADAPTIVE TUNING</text>\n          </svg>\n        );\n      default:\n        return null;\n    }\n  };\n\n  const activeChallengeObj = CHALLENGES.find((c) => c.id === inputs.primaryChallenge);\n\n  if (!mounted) {\n    return (\n      <div className=\"min-h-screen bg-[#020204] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-mono text-xs\">\n        Booting GFF Enterprise proposal workspace...\n      </div>\n    );\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <ToolPageShell showContact={step !== \"preview\"}>\n      \n      {/* 1. HERO HEADER AREA */}\n      <ToolHero\n        category=\"PHASE 3 // STRATEGIC ADVISORY SOW BUILDER\"\n        title=\"Sovereign AI Proposal\"\n        highlightedWord=\"Proposal\"\n        description=\"Configure strategic integration models, design multi-agent topologies, and compile localized statement of work (SOW) blueprints completely offline.\"\n      />\n\n      <AnimatePresence mode=\"wait\">\n\n        {/* 2. INTAKE CONFIGURATION WORKSPACE */}\n        {step === \"configure\" && (\n          <motion.div\n            initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 12 }}\n            animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\n            exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -12 }}\n            transition={{ duration: 0.3, ease: \"easeOut\" }}\n            className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\"\n          >\n            {/* LEFT AREA: FORM PANEL (8 columns) */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-8 space-y-6\">\n              \n              {/* Draft restoration panel */}\n              {hasSavedDraft && (\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-[#009DFF]/20 bg-[#009DFF]/5 flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-white\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                    <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-pulse\" />\n                    <span>In-progress draft detected from your previous workspace session.</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n                    <button onClick={handleRestoreDraft} className=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/25 border border-[#009DFF]/40 text-[#009DFF] text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-[#009DFF]/40 transition uppercase font-bold\">Restore Draft</button>\n                    <button onClick={() => setHasSavedDraft(false)} className=\"px-2 py-1.5 text-white/40 text-[10px] font-mono hover:text-white uppercase\">Ignore</button>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* STEP TIMELINE GATE HEADER */}\n              <div className=\"p-1 rounded-lg bg-black/40 border border-white/5 flex text-center text-[10px] font-mono\">\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={() => { if (validateStep(1)) setActiveStepGate(1); }}\n                  className={`flex-1 py-2 rounded-md transition font-semibold uppercase ${activeStepGate === 1 ? \"bg-white/5 text-[#009DFF] border border-white/10\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"}`}\n                >\n                  01 // Corporate Baseline\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={() => { if (activeStepGate > 1 && validateStep(1)) setActiveStepGate(2); }}\n                  className={`flex-1 py-2 rounded-md transition font-semibold uppercase ${activeStepGate === 2 ? \"bg-white/5 text-[#009DFF] border border-white/10\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"}`}\n                  disabled={activeStepGate < 2 && !validateStep(1)}\n                >\n                  02 // Strategic Challenge\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  onClick={() => { if (activeStepGate > 2 && validateStep(1) && validateStep(2)) setActiveStepGate(3); }}\n                  className={`flex-1 py-2 rounded-md transition font-semibold uppercase ${activeStepGate === 3 ? \"bg-white/5 text-[#009DFF] border border-white/10\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"}`}\n                  disabled={activeStepGate < 3 && (!validateStep(1) || !validateStep(2))}\n                >\n                  03 // Deployment pathway\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* FORM WRAPPER CARD */}\n              <div className=\"p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 relative overflow-hidden\">\n                <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 font-mono text-[9px] text-white/25\">\n                  GFF_PROPOSAL_STUDIO // REV_2026\n                </div>\n\n                {/* ==========================================\n                    STEP GATE 1: CORPORATE BASELINE\n                    ========================================== */}\n                {activeStepGate === 1 && (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">GATE 01 OF 03</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mt-1\">Corporate Baseline Profile</h2>\n                      <p className=\"text-white/40 text-xs mt-1\">Establish your organizational metadata, industry taxonomy, and geographical boundaries.</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* FIELD 1: ORGANIZATION NAME (Optional) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide\">Organization Name</label>\n                        <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">Optional</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <input\n                        type=\"text\"\n                        value={inputs.companyName}\n                        onChange={(e) => setInputs({ ...inputs, companyName: e.target.value })}\n                        placeholder=\"e.g. Sovereign Global Mainframes\"\n                        className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 h-11 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#009DFF]/30 transition\"\n                      />\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* FIELD 2: INDUSTRY VERTICAL (Required Selection Grid) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide\">Industry Vertical</label>\n                        {validationErrors.industry && <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{validationErrors.industry}</span>}\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n                        {INDUSTRIES.map((ind) => (\n                          <button\n                            key={ind.id}\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={() => {\n                              setInputs({ ...inputs, industry: ind.id });\n                              setValidationErrors((prev) => ({ ...prev, industry: \"\" }));\n                            }}\n                            className={`p-3.5 rounded-xl border text-left transition flex gap-3.5 items-start min-h-[75px] ${inputs.industry === ind.id ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(0,157,255,0.12)]\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-black/60\"}`}\n                          >\n                            <span className=\"text-lg mt-0.5\">{ind.icon}</span>\n                            <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                              <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white leading-none\">{ind.label}</h4>\n                              <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 leading-snug font-light\">{ind.desc}</p>\n                            </div>\n                          </button>\n                        ))}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* FIELD 3: COMPANY SIZE (Required Cards) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide\">Enterprise Operational Scale</label>\n                        {validationErrors.companySize && <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{validationErrors.companySize}</span>}\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n                        {COMPANY_SIZES.map((size) => (\n                          <button\n                            key={size.id}\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={() => {\n                              setInputs({ ...inputs, companySize: size.id });\n                              setValidationErrors((prev) => ({ ...prev, companySize: \"\" }));\n                            }}\n                            className={`p-3 rounded-xl border text-left transition flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[105px] ${inputs.companySize === size.id ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-white/10\"}`}\n                          >\n                            <div>\n                              <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white leading-tight\">{size.label}</h4>\n                              <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/45 uppercase mt-0.5 block\">{size.range}</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 leading-tight font-light mt-1.5\">{size.desc}</p>\n                          </button>\n                        ))}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* FIELD 4: GEOGRAPHY (Optional Input) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide\">Deployment Geography</label>\n                        <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold\">Optional</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <input\n                        type=\"text\"\n                        value={inputs.geography}\n                        onChange={(e) => setInputs({ ...inputs, geography: e.target.value })}\n                        placeholder=\"e.g. EU Sovereign Boundary (VPC Frankfurt), AWS us-east-1 VPC\"\n                        className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 h-11 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#009DFF]/30 transition\"\n                      />\n                      <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 leading-normal\">Defines the secure perimeter boundaries to ensure zero external logging endpoints.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n\n                {/* ==========================================\n                    STEP GATE 2: CHALLENGE & PRIORITIES\n                    ========================================== */}\n                {activeStepGate === 2 && (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">GATE 02 OF 03</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mt-1\">Strategic Friction & Outcomes</h2>\n                      <p className=\"text-white/40 text-xs mt-1 font-light\">Isolate the primary organizational challenges and map specific priority target outcomes.</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* FIELD 5: PRIMARY CHALLENGE (Cards) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide\">Primary Obstacle</label>\n                        {validationErrors.primaryChallenge && <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{validationErrors.primaryChallenge}</span>}\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                        {CHALLENGES.map((chal) => (\n                          <button\n                            key={chal.id}\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={() => {\n                              setInputs({ ...inputs, primaryChallenge: chal.id });\n                              setValidationErrors((prev) => ({ ...prev, primaryChallenge: \"\" }));\n                            }}\n                            className={`p-3.5 rounded-xl border text-left transition flex gap-3.5 items-start min-h-[85px] ${inputs.primaryChallenge === chal.id ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(0,157,255,0.08)]\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-white/10\"}`}\n                          >\n                            <span className=\"text-base mt-0.5\">{chal.icon}</span>\n                            <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                              <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white leading-none\">{chal.label}</h4>\n                              <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 leading-relaxed font-light\">{chal.desc}</p>\n                            </div>\n                          </button>\n                        ))}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* DYNAMIC FIELD: CUSTOM CHALLENGE INPUT (Visible only if other selected) */}\n                    {inputs.primaryChallenge === \"other\" && (\n                      <motion.div\n                        initial={{ opacity: 0, height: 0 }}\n                        animate={{ opacity: 1, height: \"auto\" }}\n                        className=\"space-y-1.5\"\n                      >\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide block\">Specify Custom Obstacle</label>\n                        <textarea\n                          rows={2}\n                          value={inputs.customChallenge}\n                          onChange={(e) => {\n                            setInputs({ ...inputs, customChallenge: e.target.value });\n                            setValidationErrors((prev) => ({ ...prev, customChallenge: \"\" }));\n                          }}\n                          placeholder=\"Describe the technical or organizational barrier we must architecturalize against...\"\n                          className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 transition\"\n                        />\n                        {validationErrors.customChallenge && <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] block font-bold\">{validationErrors.customChallenge}</span>}\n                      </motion.div>\n                    )}\n\n                    {/* FIELD 6: PRIORITY OUTCOMES (Checkbox Grid Multi-Select) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide\">Priority Target Outcomes (Select at least one)</label>\n                        {validationErrors.priorityOutcomes && <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{validationErrors.priorityOutcomes}</span>}\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                        {OUTCOMES.map((out) => {\n                          const isSelected = inputs.priorityOutcomes.includes(out.id);\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={out.id}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => {\n                                let list = [...inputs.priorityOutcomes];\n                                if (isSelected) {\n                                  list = list.filter((id) => id !== out.id);\n                                } else {\n                                  list.push(out.id);\n                                }\n                                setInputs({ ...inputs, priorityOutcomes: list });\n                                setValidationErrors((prev) => ({ ...prev, priorityOutcomes: \"\" }));\n                              }}\n                              className={`p-3 rounded-xl border text-left transition flex items-center justify-between gap-4 ${isSelected ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-white/10\"}`}\n                            >\n                              <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white leading-tight\">{out.label}</h4>\n                                <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 leading-tight font-light\">{out.desc}</p>\n                              </div>\n                              <div className={`w-4 h-4 rounded border flex items-center justify-center transition-all ${isSelected ? \"bg-[#009DFF] border-[#009DFF]\" : \"border-white/20 bg-black/50\"}`}>\n                                {isSelected && (\n                                  <svg className=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 text-black\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth={3}>\n                                    <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" />\n                                  </svg>\n                                )}\n                              </div>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* FIELD 7: TARGET TIMELINE (Timeline selector) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide\">Target Project Timeline</label>\n                        {validationErrors.targetTimeline && <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{validationErrors.targetTimeline}</span>}\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n                        {TIMELINES.map((t) => (\n                          <button\n                            key={t.id}\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={() => {\n                              setInputs({ ...inputs, targetTimeline: t.id });\n                              setValidationErrors((prev) => ({ ...prev, targetTimeline: \"\" }));\n                            }}\n                            className={`p-3 rounded-xl border text-left transition flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[90px] ${inputs.targetTimeline === t.id ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-white/10\"}`}\n                          >\n                            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white leading-tight\">{t.label}</h4>\n                            <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 leading-tight font-light mt-1.5\">{t.desc}</p>\n                          </button>\n                        ))}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n\n                {/* ==========================================\n                    STEP GATE 3: DEPLOYMENT PATHWAY\n                    ========================================== */}\n                {activeStepGate === 3 && (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">GATE 03 OF 03</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mt-1\">Sovereign Engagement Pathway</h2>\n                      <p className=\"text-white/40 text-xs mt-1\">Select the operational integration path, specify sponsor stakeholders, and outline capital allocation ranges.</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* FIELD 8: PREFERRED ENGAGEMENT PATH (Sleek Figma Cards) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-2.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide block\">Strategic Integration Path</label>\n                        {validationErrors.preferredEngagementPath && <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{validationErrors.preferredEngagementPath}</span>}\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                        {ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.map((path) => {\n                          const isSelected = inputs.preferredEngagementPath === path.id;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={path.id}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => {\n                                setInputs({ ...inputs, preferredEngagementPath: path.id });\n                                setValidationErrors((prev) => ({ ...prev, preferredEngagementPath: \"\" }));\n                              }}\n                              className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[175px] relative overflow-hidden ${isSelected ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#030307]\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-white/10\"}`}\n                              style={{\n                                boxShadow: isSelected ? `0 0 15px -3px ${path.accent}25` : \"none\"\n                              }}\n                            >\n                              {/* Selection overlay color indicator */}\n                              <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full\" style={{ backgroundColor: path.accent }} />\n\n                              <div className=\"pl-2 space-y-1\">\n                                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                                  <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono uppercase font-bold tracking-widest px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded\" style={{ color: path.accent, backgroundColor: `${path.accent}15` }}>{path.badge}</span>\n                                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">{path.weeks}</span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h3 className=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-white mt-1.5\">{path.label}</h3>\n                                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/45 leading-relaxed mt-1 font-light\">{path.desc}</p>\n                              </div>\n\n                              <div className=\"pl-2 pt-3 mt-3 border-t border-white/5 text-[9px] font-mono space-y-0.5 text-white/30\">\n                                <div><span className=\"text-white/50 font-semibold\">SQUAD CONFIG:</span> {path.squad}</div>\n                                <div><span className=\"text-white/50 font-semibold\">PRIMARY OUTCOME:</span> <span className=\"text-white/70\">{path.outcome}</span></div>\n                              </div>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* FIELD 9: BUDGET RANGE (Optional) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide block\">Capital Allocation Target Range</label>\n                        <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">Optional</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n                        {BUDGET_RANGES.map((b) => (\n                          <button\n                            key={b.id}\n                            type=\"button\"\n                            onClick={() => setInputs({ ...inputs, budgetRange: b.id })}\n                            className={`p-3 rounded-xl border text-left transition ${inputs.budgetRange === b.id ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-white/10\"}`}\n                          >\n                            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white leading-tight\">{b.label}</h4>\n                            <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 leading-tight font-light mt-1.5\">{b.desc}</p>\n                          </button>\n                        ))}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* FIELD 10: STAKEHOLDERS (Optional) */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/55 uppercase tracking-wide block\">Sponsor Stakeholders</label>\n                        <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">Optional</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <input\n                        type=\"text\"\n                        value={inputs.stakeholders}\n                        onChange={(e) => setInputs({ ...inputs, stakeholders: e.target.value })}\n                        placeholder=\"e.g. VP of Security Audit, Lead AI Compliance Architect, Chief Data Officer\"\n                        className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 h-11 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#009DFF]/30 transition\"\n                      />\n                      <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 leading-normal\">Helps customize administration bounds, access governance hierarchies, and delivery parameters.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n\n                {/* STEPS NAVIGATION BUTTONS */}\n                <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-6 mt-8 flex justify-between items-center\">\n                  <button\n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={() => setActiveStepGate((prev) => (prev - 1) as 1 | 2 | 3)}\n                    disabled={activeStepGate === 1}\n                    className={`px-4 h-10 rounded-lg border text-xs font-mono uppercase flex items-center gap-1 transition ${activeStepGate === 1 ? \"border-white/5 text-white/10 cursor-not-allowed\" : \"border-white/10 text-white hover:bg-white/5\"}`}\n                  >\n                    Back\n                  </button>\n                  <div className=\"flex gap-3\">\n                    <button\n                      type=\"button\"\n                      onClick={handleSaveDraft}\n                      className=\"px-4 h-10 rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-xs font-mono text-white hover:bg-white/5 transition uppercase\"\n                    >\n                      {saved ? \"✓ Saved\" : \"[ Save Draft ]\"}\n                    </button>\n                    {activeStepGate < 3 ? (\n                      <button\n                        type=\"button\"\n                        onClick={handleNextGate}\n                        className=\"px-5 h-10 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold uppercase bg-[#009DFF] text-black hover:bg-[#009DFF]/90 font-mono shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.25)]\"\n                      >\n                        Next Gate\n                      </button>\n                    ) : (\n                      <button\n                        type=\"button\"\n                        onClick={handleCompile}\n                        className=\"px-5 h-10 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold uppercase bg-[#00FF9D] text-black hover:bg-[#00FF9D]/90 font-mono shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,255,157,0.25)]\"\n                      >\n                        Sovereign Compile\n                      </button>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* RIGHT AREA: STICKY LIVE OUTLINE PREVIEW PANEL (4 columns) */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-4 lg:sticky lg:top-8 space-y-4 hidden lg:block\">\n              <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 text-left relative\">\n                {/* Telemetry flashing dot */}\n                <div className=\"absolute top-4 right-4 flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9D] animate-ping\" />\n                  <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">LIVE COMPILING</span>\n                </div>\n\n                <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/35 font-bold uppercase block mb-3\">SOW compilation blueprint</span>\n\n                <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                  {/* Entity Metadata */}\n                  <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg bg-black/60 border border-white/5 font-mono text-[9.5px] leading-relaxed space-y-1.5 text-white/60\">\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase\">ENTITY:</span>{\" \"}\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{pData.org}</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase\">VERTICAL:</span>{\" \"}\n                      <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-semibold\">{pData.industryLabel}</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase\">SCALE RANGE:</span>{\" \"}\n                      <span className=\"text-white/80\">{pData.companySizeLabel} ({pData.companySizeRange})</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase\">VPC REGION:</span>{\" \"}\n                      <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">{inputs.geography.trim() ? pData.geographyLabel : \"Unspecified VPC boundary\"}</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* SOW Draft Checklist */}\n                  <div className=\"space-y-2.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider block\">INTEGRATION GATEWAYS STATUS</span>\n                    <ul className=\"space-y-1.5 font-mono text-[9px] text-white/50\">\n                      <li className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">✓</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/85\">Gate 1: Baseline established</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                        <span className={activeStepGate >= 2 ? \"text-[#00FF9D]\" : \"text-white/20\"}>\n                          {activeStepGate >= 2 ? \"✓\" : \"○\"}\n                        </span>\n                        <span className={activeStepGate >= 2 ? \"text-white/85\" : \"text-white/30\"}>Gate 2: Friction & Priorities configured</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                        <span className={activeStepGate >= 3 ? \"text-[#00FF9D]\" : \"text-white/20\"}>\n                          {activeStepGate >= 3 ? \"✓\" : \"○\"}\n                        </span>\n                        <span className={activeStepGate >= 3 ? \"text-white/85\" : \"text-white/30\"}>Gate 3: Engagement path resolved</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* live outline draft list */}\n                  <div className=\"pt-3.5 border-t border-white/5 space-y-2\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider block\">PROPOSAL SOW OUTLINE</span>\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1 text-[10px] text-white/40 leading-snug\">\n                      <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n                        <span className=\"font-mono text-[#009DFF]\">SEC I.</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/70\">Executive Summary // {pData.industryLabel} Context</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n                        <span className=\"font-mono text-[#009DFF]\">SEC II.</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/70\">Hardened Boundary ({pData.geographyLabel.substring(0, 18)}...)</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n                        <span className=\"font-mono text-[#009DFF]\">SEC III.</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/70\">Deployment Model // {pData.engagementPathObj.label} Model</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n                        <span className=\"font-mono text-[#009DFF]\">SEC IV.</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/70\">Workstreams & Milestones ({pData.weeks} Weeks)</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </motion.div>\n        )}\n\n        {/* 3. CO-INNOVATION COMPILING STATE */}\n        {step === \"compiling\" && (\n          <motion.div\n            key=\"compiling\"\n            initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.98 }}\n            animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1 }}\n            exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 1.02 }}\n            className=\"max-w-xl mx-auto p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[380px] text-center\"\n          >\n            <div className=\"relative w-16 h-16 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center\">\n              <div className=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-[#00FF9D]/20 animate-ping\" />\n              <div className=\"absolute inset-2 rounded-full border border-[#009DFF]/30 animate-pulse\" />\n              <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-black border border-[#00FF9D]/80 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9D] animate-ping\" />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] font-bold tracking-widest block mb-1\">SOVEREIGN COMPILER v4.26</span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4\">Compiling Custom Proposal SOW</h2>\n\n            <div className=\"w-full p-4 rounded-lg bg-black/60 border border-white/5 text-left mb-4 relative overflow-hidden\">\n              <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 h-0.5 bg-[#009DFF] transition-all duration-300\" style={{ width: `${((compilingStepIndex + 1) / compilingMessages.length) * 100}%` }} />\n              <div className=\"flex gap-2 font-mono text-[9px] text-white/50\">\n                <span className=\"text-[#009DFF]\">&gt;</span>\n                <p className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-semibold leading-relaxed\">{compilingMessages[compilingStepIndex]}</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <p className=\"text-white/30 text-[9px] font-mono\">ZERO DATA RETENTION LAYER GUARANTEED</p>\n          </motion.div>\n        )}\n\n        {/* 4. EXECUTIVE PROPOSAL VIEWPORT */}\n        {step === \"preview\" && (\n          <motion.div\n            key=\"preview\"\n            initial={{ opacity: 0 }}\n            animate={{ opacity: 1 }}\n            className=\"space-y-6\"\n          >\n            <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n              \n              {/* INDEX COLUMN (3 columns) */}\n              <div className=\"lg:col-span-3 space-y-4 sticky top-6 print:hidden\">\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 text-left\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/35 font-bold block mb-3\">DOSSIER INDEX</span>\n                  <nav className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                    {[\n                      { id: \"executive-summary\", label: \"Executive Summary\", icon: \"📄\" },\n                      { id: \"geographical-scope\", label: \"Hardened Perimeter Setup\", icon: \"🔍\" },\n                      { id: \"recommended-gff-path\", label: \"Deployment Model\", icon: \"🚀\" },\n                      { id: \"proposed-workstreams\", label: \"Delivery Phases\", icon: \"🗺️\" },\n                      { id: \"success-measures\", label: \"Strategic Outcome metrics\", icon: \"📈\" },\n                      { id: \"sign-off-block\", label: \"Executive Signature\", icon: \"✍️\" }\n                    ].map((sec, idx) => (\n                      <button\n                        key={sec.id}\n                        onClick={() => {\n                          setActivePreviewSection(sec.id);\n                          const el = document.getElementById(sec.id);\n                          if (el) el.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \"smooth\", block: \"start\" });\n                        }}\n                        className={`w-full text-left px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-[11px] transition flex items-center gap-2 ${activePreviewSection === sec.id ? \"bg-white/5 text-[#009DFF] font-bold border-l border-[#009DFF]\" : \"text-white/50 hover:text-white\"}`}\n                      >\n                        <span>{sec.icon}</span>\n                        <span>{idx + 1}. {sec.label}</span>\n                      </button>\n                    ))}\n                  </nav>\n\n                  <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 space-y-2\">\n                    <button onClick={handleCopyOutline} className=\"w-full py-2 rounded bg-white/5 text-white border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 transition text-[9px] font-mono uppercase font-semibold\">\n                      {copied ? \"✓ Copied\" : \"Copy Outline\"}\n                    </button>\n                    <button onClick={handlePrint} className=\"w-full py-2 rounded bg-white/5 text-white border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 transition text-[9px] font-mono uppercase font-semibold\">\n                      Print Spec Preview\n                    </button>\n                    <button onClick={handleReset} className=\"w-full py-1 text-center text-white/30 text-[9px] font-mono hover:text-white block uppercase\">\n                      [ Clear Form & Restart ]\n                    </button>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/80 text-[10px] text-white/40 space-y-2 text-left\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">WORKSPACE</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono bg-[#E4000F]/15 text-[#E4000F] px-1 rounded font-bold\">PREVIEW LAYER</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <h4 className=\"font-bold text-white leading-tight\">Full SOW & PDF Exports</h4>\n                  <p className=\"font-light leading-snug\">To download real-world contract-ready PDF SOW templates or enterprise presentation slides, please coordinate directly with your GFF Account Fleet coordinator.</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* CENTER COLUMN: FULL SOW PREVIEW (9 columns) */}\n              <div className=\"lg:col-span-9 p-6 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/85 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden print:bg-white print:text-black print:p-0 print:border-none\" id=\"proposal-document-content\">\n                \n                <div className=\"hidden print:block text-right text-[8px] font-mono text-black/40 mb-6 border-b border-black/10 pb-1\">\n                  <span>GFF AI CONFIDENTIAL PORTFOLIO // SOVEREIGN SPECIFICATION ARCHITECTURE</span>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"border-b border-white/10 pb-6 mb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-4 print:border-black/20\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-2 text-left\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9D] print:bg-black\" />\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold print:text-black/60\">STATEMENT OF WORK OUTLINE</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h1 className=\"text-xl lg:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white print:text-black tracking-tight leading-none\">\n                      {pData.org} Sovereign Integration\n                    </h1>\n                    <p className=\"text-white/60 text-xs font-light max-w-lg print:text-black/70\">\n                      Tailored technical deployment blueprint and architectural SOW outline for <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.org}</strong>.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 flex flex-col items-end text-right min-w-[170px] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">IMPLEMENTATION HORIZON</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-base font-bold text-white font-mono print:text-black\">{pData.weeks} WEEKS</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] mt-0.5 uppercase font-bold\">{pData.budgetLabel}</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* SOW TEXT BODY SECTIONS */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-12 print:space-y-10 text-left\">\n                  \n                  {/* SECTION 1: EXECUTIVE SUMMARY */}\n                  <div id=\"executive-summary\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION I</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5\">📄 Executive Summary</h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-3 print:text-black/85\">\n                      <p>\n                        This document details the strategic, sovereign deployment architecture mapped for integrating GFF AI systems within the operational boundary of <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.org}</strong>. Operating within the <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.industryLabel}</strong> sector, GFF AI will construct a dedicated private environment designed to resolve the primary challenge: <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.challengeLabel}</strong>.\n                      </p>\n                      <p>\n                        The deployment enforces zero-retention data logging pipelines, validating compliance with strict internal policies. All operations, queries, and integrations will be structured within isolated memory namespaces, compressing latency and locking down structural security boundaries.\n                      </p>\n\n                      <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between sm:items-center gap-4 print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/[0.01]\">\n                        <div className=\"text-left space-y-1\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[7px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block print:text-black/50 font-semibold\">SECURITY PROFILE ENFORCED</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-white/80 text-[10px] font-light print:text-black\">Hardened Private VPC boundary featuring real-time automated audit-trail telemetry.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n                          <div className=\"text-center p-2 rounded bg-black/40 min-w-[80px] border border-white/5 print:border-black/10\">\n                            <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#00FF9D] block font-mono print:text-black\">100%</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[6px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase print:text-black/60\">VPC Isolated</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <div className=\"text-center p-2 rounded bg-black/40 min-w-[80px] border border-white/5 print:border-black/10\">\n                            <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#009DFF] block font-mono print:text-black\">0</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[6px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase print:text-black/60\">Retained Logs</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* SECTION 2: GEOGRAPHICAL & STAKEHOLDER SCOPE */}\n                  <div id=\"geographical-scope\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION II</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5\">🔍 Hardened Perimeter Setup</h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-3 print:text-black/85\">\n                      <p>\n                        To guarantee complete data confidentiality and mitigate risk, all system interfaces will be deployed exclusively inside the designated region: <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.geographyLabel}</strong>. There will be no data transmission outside this perimeter.\n                      </p>\n                      \n                      {/* Stakeholder table or detail */}\n                      <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/40 print:border-black/10\">\n                        <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1.5 font-mono uppercase tracking-wide\">ADMINISTRATIVE BOUNDS & SPONSORS</h4>\n                        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-[10px]\">\n                          <div>\n                            <span className=\"text-white/30 font-mono block\">SPONSOR STAKEHOLDERS:</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white font-medium print:text-black\">{pData.stakeholdersLabel}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <div>\n                            <span className=\"text-white/30 font-mono block\">VERTICAL OVERVIEW:</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white font-medium print:text-black\">{pData.industryLabel} ({pData.companySizeLabel} scale)</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* SECTION 3: RECOMMENDED GFF DEPLOYMENT MODEL */}\n                  <div id=\"recommended-gff-path\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION III</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5\">🚀 Deployment & Engagement Model</h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n                      <p>\n                        GFF AI recommends the <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.engagementPathObj.label}</strong> engagement pathway to deliver secure, industrialized cognitive capabilities within your environment:\n                      </p>\n\n                      {/* ARCHITECTURE DIAGRAM METAPHOR */}\n                      <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest block font-bold\">SOVEREIGN ACTIVE DEPLOYMENT ARCHITECTURE PLAN</span>\n                        {renderTopologyDiagram(inputs.preferredEngagementPath)}\n                      </div>\n\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-2\">\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/30 print:border-black/10 text-left\">\n                          <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1 uppercase font-mono tracking-wide\">Delivery Fleet Sizing</h4>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/40 leading-relaxed print:text-black/70\">\n                            Our team configuration targets rapid engineering, assigning: <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.engagementPathObj.squad}</strong>.\n                          </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/30 print:border-black/10 text-left\">\n                          <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1 uppercase font-mono tracking-wide\">Core Objective Delivery</h4>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/40 leading-relaxed print:text-black/70\">\n                            The milestone outcome of this contract phase is: <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.engagementPathObj.outcome}</strong>.\n                          </p>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* SECTION 4: PROJECT WORKSTREAMS & DELIVERABLES */}\n                  <div id=\"proposed-workstreams\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION IV</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5\">🗺️ Strategic Delivery Phases</h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n                      <p>\n                        Technical delivery and setup objectives are divided into four clear workstreams mapped to your target timeline of <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.weeks} Weeks</strong>:\n                      </p>\n\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3.5\">\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/40 space-y-1 print:border-black/10 text-left\">\n                          <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                            <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-bold text-white print:text-black\">Workstream A: Hardened Perimeter Setup</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[8.5px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">WEEKS 1 - {pData.p1}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 print:text-black/70 font-light\">Provision isolated single-tenant private virtual enclaves, establish secure networking perimeters, and verify local data retention compliance rules.</p>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/40 space-y-1 print:border-black/10 text-left\">\n                          <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                            <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-bold text-white print:text-black\">Workstream B: Ingestion & Connection Integration</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[8.5px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">WEEKS {pData.p1 + 1} - {pData.p1 + pData.p2}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 print:text-black/70 font-light\">Establish OmniMesh read-only connections to local databases and structured schemas. Mount localized secure context semantic cache pipelines.</p>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/40 space-y-1 print:border-black/10 text-left\">\n                          <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                            <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-bold text-white print:text-black\">Workstream C: Consensus Node Fine-Tuning</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[8.5px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">WEEKS {pData.p1 + pData.p2 + 1} - {pData.p1 + pData.p2 + pData.p3}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 print:text-black/70 font-light\">Configure customized agent topologies, compile consensus decision-loop modules, and validate model response safety parameters.</p>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/40 space-y-1 print:border-black/10 text-left\">\n                          <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                            <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-bold text-white print:text-black\">Workstream D: Validation & SLA Lock</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[8.5px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">WEEKS {pData.p1 + pData.p2 + pData.p3 + 1} - {pData.weeks}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 print:text-black/70 font-light\">Enforce target compliance policies, measure sub-150ms execution rates under high token volume, and initiate co-innovation transfer handoff.</p>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n\n                      {/* Explicit list of contract deliverables */}\n                      <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/[0.01]\">\n                        <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-2 uppercase font-mono tracking-wider\">CONTRACTUAL DELIVERABLES LOG:</h4>\n                        <ul className=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[9.5px] text-white/50 print:text-black/80 font-light\">\n                          {pData.deliverables.map((del, idx) => (\n                            <li key={idx}><strong>Deliverable {idx + 1}:</strong> {del}</li>\n                          ))}\n                        </ul>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* SECTION 5: SUCCESS MEASURES */}\n                  <div id=\"success-measures\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION V</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5\">📈 Strategic Success Measures</h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-3 print:text-black/85\">\n                      <p>Compliance and operational performance targets are tracked dynamically using our sovereign consensus dashboard system:</p>\n                      \n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3.5 text-center font-mono\">\n                        <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n                          <span className=\"text-sm font-bold text-[#00FF9D] block print:text-black\">&gt; 99.9%</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block print:text-black/60\">Task Success</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n                          <span className=\"text-sm font-bold text-[#009DFF] block print:text-black\">&lt; 150ms</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block print:text-black/60\">Execution Latency</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n                          <span className=\"text-sm font-bold text-[#9D00FF] block print:text-black\">0</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block print:text-black/60\">Telemetry IP Leaks</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n                          <span className=\"text-sm font-bold text-[#E5A93C] block print:text-black\">30%+</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block print:text-black/60\">SaaS Reclaimed</span>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n\n                      {/* Selected target outcome summary panel */}\n                      <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/40 text-[9.5px] leading-relaxed text-white/50 print:border-black/10\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/35 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider block mb-1\">Target Outcomes Included:</span>\n                        {pData.selectedOutcomeLabels.join(\" // \")}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* SECTION 6: EXECUTIVE SIGN-OFF BLOCK */}\n                  <div id=\"sign-off-block\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION VI</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5\">✍️ Executive Signature</h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n                      <p>\n                        This SOW blueprint serves as an architectural planning draft. Signing validates strategic intent to proceed with sandbox provisioning or systems planning matching these configurations.\n                      </p>\n\n                      <div className=\"p-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-black/35 print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/[0.01] max-w-lg\">\n                        {!isSigned ? (\n                          <div className=\"space-y-3.5 text-left\">\n                            <h4 className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider print:text-black\">SIGN SOW PLAN</h4>\n                            <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                              <input\n                                type=\"text\"\n                                placeholder=\"Type Full Name to Authorize\"\n                                value={signName}\n                                onChange={(e) => setSignName(e.target.value)}\n                                className=\"w-full bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-3.5 h-10 text-xs text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]\"\n                              />\n                              <input\n                                type=\"text\"\n                                placeholder=\"Type Corporate Title\"\n                                value={signTitle}\n                                onChange={(e) => setSignTitle(e.target.value)}\n                                className=\"w-full bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-3.5 h-10 text-xs text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]\"\n                              />\n                            </div>\n                            <button\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => {\n                                if (signName.trim() && signTitle.trim()) {\n                                  setIsSigned(true);\n                                } else {\n                                  alert(\"Please provide both name and corporate title to authorize the SOW blueprint.\");\n                                }\n                              }}\n                              className=\"w-full py-2 bg-[#00FF9D] text-black rounded-lg text-xs font-mono uppercase font-bold hover:bg-[#00FF9D]/90 transition\"\n                            >\n                              Authorize strategic draft\n                            </button>\n                          </div>\n                        ) : (\n                          <motion.div\n                            initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.95 }}\n                            animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1 }}\n                            className=\"space-y-4 text-left\"\n                          >\n                            <div className=\"border border-dashed border-[#00FF9D]/40 p-4 rounded-xl bg-[#00FF9D]/5 flex justify-between items-start\">\n                              <div className=\"space-y-1.5 font-mono text-[9px] text-[#00FF9D]\">\n                                <span className=\"text-[7.5px] bg-[#00FF9D]/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">SOW_AUTHORIZED_SECURE</span>\n                                <div><strong>SPONSOR:</strong> {signName}</div>\n                                <div><strong>TITLE:</strong> {signTitle}</div>\n                                <div><strong>TIMESTAMP:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleString()}</div>\n                              </div>\n                              <div className=\"p-2 border border-[#00FF9D]/50 rounded text-center text-[8px] font-mono font-bold text-[#00FF9D] select-none rotate-6\">\n                                GFF SEAL // SECURE\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30\">\n                              <span>SHA-256 COMPLIANCE STAMP: 8f9b93e...</span>\n                              <button onClick={() => setIsSigned(false)} className=\"text-[#E4000F] hover:underline uppercase\">[ Revoke ]</button>\n                            </div>\n                          </motion.div>\n                        )}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"mt-12 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 text-center text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30 flex justify-between items-center print:border-black/10 print:text-black/50\">\n                  <span>GFF COGNITIVE PROPOSAL TERMINAL // v4.26-REV</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] print:text-black font-semibold\">SOVEREIGN COMPLIANT // LOCAL DEPLOY READY</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n          </motion.div>\n        )}\n\n      </AnimatePresence>\n\n    </ToolPageShell>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
