y accurately with each button click. I'm exploring efficient ways to manage potential validation errors and presenting them concisely.\n\n\n**Improving Button Logic**\n\nI'm now focusing on streamlining the `priorityOutcomes` button logic within the JSX. My aim is to make the `isSelected` state management more efficient and concise. I'm prioritizing accurate state updates for the `inputs.priorityOutcomes` array with each click, while managing potential validation errors effectively. I want the button's visual feedback to be seamless and intuitive.\n\n\n"}}
